  "en": {
    "title": "history - Command history list",
    "synopsis": "history",
    "description": "List previous commands entered in the current session.",
    "details": "NAME\n  history - Command history list.\n\nSYNOPSIS\n  history\n\nDESCRIPTION\n  Displays the list of commands entered in the current terminal session.\n\nSYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\n  Reads from the global 'hist' array stored in RAM. The queue is bounded to a maximum of 100 commands.\n\nEXIT CODES\n  0\n    Success.\n\nCONFORMING TO\n  NucleoOS extension compatible with POSIX.\n\nAUTHOR\n  NucleoOS Core Devs.\n\nREPORTING BUGS\n  Report bugs to support@nucleoos.org.\n\nSEE ALSO\n  clear(1)\n\nADVANCED EXAMPLES\n  history"
